---
import ArticleLayout from '../../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
import Button from '../../components/Button.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<ArticleLayout
  title="5 Ways to Celebrate Easter as a Family"
  author="Catherine Renneberg"
  date="January 2026"
  category="Resource"
  authorImage="/images/people/Catherine-Renneberg-headshot.jpg"
  image="/images/art/caravaggio-supper-emmaus.jpg"
  imageAlt="Supper at Emmaus by Caravaggio, 1601"
  related={[
    { title: "Christmas Book Recommendations 2025", href: `${base}library/christmas-books-2025/`, meta: "Resource · GGI" },
    { title: "The Abolition of Man Study Guide", href: `${base}library/abolition-of-man-guide/`, meta: "Resource · GGI" },
  ]}
>
  <p>
    Easter is the centre of the Christian year — the feast that gives meaning to everything
    else. But in a culture that moves quickly from one holiday to the next, it can be
    difficult to give the Paschal season the attention it deserves, especially with children.
  </p>

  <p>
    This short guide offers five practical ideas for families looking to deepen their
    celebration of Easter at home. From simple traditions to liturgical practices, these
    suggestions are designed to help families — whether just starting out or looking for
    new ways to mark the season — enter more deeply into the mystery of the Resurrection.
  </p>

  <div class="resource-download">
    <h3 class="resource-download__heading">Get this resource</h3>
    <p class="resource-download__desc">Enter your email and we'll send you a copy.</p>
    <form class="resource-download__form" data-ac-endpoint="/api/subscribe" data-ac-success="Check your inbox for the download link!" method="POST">
      <input type="hidden" name="resource" value="easter-family" />
      <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="Email address" aria-label="Email address" />
      <button type="submit">Email Me a Copy</button>
    </form>
    <label class="resource-download__optin">
      <input type="checkbox" name="magnalia_letter" value="yes" />
      <span>I'd like to receive future resources and essays from <strong>Magnalia Letter</strong></span>
    </label>
  </div>
</ArticleLayout>

<style>
  .resource-download {
    background: var(--color-linen);
    border: 1px solid rgba(198, 160, 50, 0.3);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 28px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 28px;
  }

  .resource-download__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .resource-download__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body) !important;
    font-size: 0.88rem !important;
    color: var(--color-gray) !important;
    margin-bottom: 16px !important;
  }

  .resource-download__form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .resource-download__form :global(input[type="email"]) {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.2);
    border-radius: 3px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    min-width: 200px;
    outline: none;
  }

  .resource-download__form :global(input[type="email"]):focus {
    border-color: var(--color-gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(198, 160, 50, 0.15);
  }

  .resource-download__form :global(button) {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: var(--color-crimson);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 3px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .resource-download__form :global(button:hover) {
    background: #6b1d00;
  }

  .resource-download__optin {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .resource-download__optin :global(input[type="checkbox"]) {
    margin-top: 2px;
    accent-color: var(--color-gold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .resource-download__optin :global(strong) {
    color: var(--color-navy);
  }
</style>
